==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Guenon
<hw>Guenon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any of several long-tailed arboreal African
monkeys, of the genera <gen>Cercopithecus</gen> and
<gen>Erythrocebus</gen> (formerly classified as <gen>Cercocebus</gen>),
such as as the green monkey (<spn>Cercopithecus callitrichus</spn>) and
grivet (<spn>Cercopithecus griseo-viridis</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gueparde</ent>⟦br⟧
